-- Bank of Nova Scotia Gives Wholesale Units Scotiabank Brand Name
-- B y   C o l i n   M c C l e l l a n d
-- 2012-01-28T15:13:09Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-28/bank-of-nova-scotia-gives-wholesale-units-scotiabank-brand-name.html
Bank of Nova Scotia ,  Canada ’s third-
largest bank by assets, said it’s rebranding its wholesale
financial units under the Scotiabank banner.  Scotia Capital, ScotiaMocatta and Scotia Waterous
operations have taken on the Scotiabank name, the Toronto-based
bank said in a statement today.  The entire wholesale financial services business line will
be known as Global Banking and Markets. The division offers
securities and investment banking advice to corporate,
government and institutional clients worldwide.  Scotiabank said it has more than 30 such offices globally.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Colin McClelland in Toronto at 
 cmcclelland1@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
 David Scanlan  at 
 dscanlan@bloomberg.net . 